divs: sighting detailsin my car driving on man-o-war in lexington (toward us68 from us27), my wife and i noticed a few white streaks in the sky. thinking at first they were jet trails, i began to be more curious when i noticed about 5 or 6 in different parts of the sky ... travelling at different trajectories. i also considered shooting stars or a meteor shower, but there don't appear to be any other reports (the lyrids were the week before). so, i couldn't explain it. i did manage to snap a picture of 3 of them. i lost sight of the objects when i went into orange leaf for some frozen yogurt and i didn't regain sight of them when i came back out. picture available at *(link moved to additional evidence section -- cms\sg).
